CustomField.description: This field controls bevhariou for Assignment Group to perform Member Availablity prioritization or not.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: When checked, Assignment Group is processed in Member Availability Prioritized mode. If turned on it handles situations where Member availability constrained - i.e. only a few members available at a time and we need to assess a lot of records.
CustomField.label: Member Availability Prioritized
